data.description: Multi level 4 bedroom 2 and 1/2 bath home on large corner lot with pool located NW side. Upstairs; living room, kitchen, dining area, half bath plus 2 guest bedrooms with Jack & Jill bathroom. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinet and counter space with granite counter tops, pantry, open to dining area and natural lighting throughout. Downstairs you'll find the spacious primary bedroom, large walk-in closet in primary bathroom with dual vanities, separate shower and garden tub. 3rd guest bedroom, family room & laundry room downstairs as well. Check out the huge backyard with mature trees for extra shade, fenced in pool area and a playset that will convey. Exterior has been recently painted. Property needs some TLC & priced accordingly.
